query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS interview_feedback (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  interviewId INT NOT NULL,
  candidateId INT NOT NULL,
  rating INT NOT NULL CHECK (rating >= 1 AND rating <= 5),
  technicalSkills INT CHECK (technicalSkills >= 1 AND technicalSkills <= 5),
  communication INT CHECK (communication >= 1 AND communication <= 5),
  problemSolving INT CHECK (problemSolving >= 1 AND problemSolving <= 5),
  cultureFit INT CHECK (cultureFit >= 1 AND cultureFit <= 5),
  notes TEXT,
  recommendation ENUM('strongly_recommend', 'recommend', 'neutral', 'not_recommend') DEFAULT 'neutral',
  interviewer VARCHAR(255),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX idx_interview (interviewId),
  INDEX idx_candidate (candidateId)
)
